  # Choose an Instance
  <br>
  For on-premises deployments, based on your seat count we recommend this hardware configuration:
  <br>

  Seats |	vCPUs	 | Memory |	Storage |	Root
  :-------------:  | :-------------:  | :-------------:  | :-------------:  | :-------------:
  0-500 |	2	| 16 GB |	100 GB	| 80 GB
  500-3000 |	4 |	32 GB |	250 GB |	80 GB
  3000-5000 |	8	| 64 GB |	500 GB |	80 GB

  <br>
  For AWS deployments, based on your seat count we recommend these instance types::
  <br>

  Seat Range       | | Recommended Type
  :-------------  | :-: | :-------------
  0 - 499  |	| r3.large
  500 - 2999  |	| r3.xlarge
  3000 - 5000  |	| r3.2xlarge

